| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4790 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9aac8e2e-3d5d-5296-9206-2be6f1784dc3"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
